Package: jingle
Title: Schedule Audio Playback
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Andreas Neudecker
Maintainer: Andreas Neudecker <a.neudecker@posteo.de>
Description: This package lets you schedule playback of audio files.
    This can be used for tournaments where you have a fixed game
    length and want to play jingles at the beginning, 5 min before the
    end etc.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.3)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: data.table,
   shiny,
   shinythemes,
   shinyTime
Suggests: lintr, testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
